{{- define "submission-phase" -}}

--- SUBMISSION (MANDATORY - DO NOT SKIP) ---
After implementation and tests pass, you MUST submit for review:
1. Get commit SHA: git -C {{.Worktree}} rev-parse HEAD
2. Execute liza_submit_for_review: {"task_id": "{{.TaskID}}", "commit_sha": "<SHA from step 1>", "agent_id": "{{.AgentID}}"}
3. Verify confirmation: status changed to CODE_READY_FOR_REVIEW

❌ FAILURE MODE: Completing work, saying "ready for review", then exiting WITHOUT calling the tool.
The tool call IS the deliverable. Work without tool execution = nothing happened.
{{- end -}}
